c: 6
v: 92
t: "Ndipo ili ndi Buku lodalitsika limene tavumbulutsa, kuchitira umboni zimene zinadza ilo lisadadze kuti uchenjeze Mzinda wa Makka ndi iwo amene amakhala mouzungulira. Iwo amene ali ndi chikhulupiriro mu zamoyo umene uli nkudza amakhulupirira ilo ndipo amasamala kwambiri m’mapemphero awo"